description: Deletes the IPSet specified by the ipSetId. IPSets are called trusted IP lists in the console user interface.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the detector associated with the IPSet. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

parameters.name: IpSetId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the IPSet to delete.
